\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=63844\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:442:\"<p>In search of the best SEO keyword analysis tool to help with your search marketing efforts? Keyword analysis is the process of researching the search phrases people use to search for your brand or product. It also involves analyzing the&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/\">9 Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tools You Need to Know in 2023</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28084:\"<p>In search of the best SEO keyword analysis tool to help with your search marketing efforts?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword analysis is the process of researching the search phrases people use to search for your brand or product. It also involves analyzing the search phrases your competitors use to drive visitors to their websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-an-seo-keyword-analysis-tool\">What is an SEO Keyword Analysis Tool?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-should-you-conduct-keyword-analysis\">Why Should You Conduct Keyword Analysis?</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-drive-targeted-traffic-to-your-website\">Drive Targeted Traffic to Your Website</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-notice-search-trends\">Notice Search Trends</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-improve-conversion-rates\">Improve Conversion Rates</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool-8-amazing-tools-to-choose-from\">The Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tool: Our Top Picks</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-semrush\">2. Semrush</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-ahrefs\">3. Ahrefs</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-serpstat\">4. Serpstat</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-kwfinder-by-mangools\">5. KWFinder by Mangools</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-long-tail-pro\">6. Long Tail Pro</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-moz-keyword-explorer\">7. Moz Keyword Explorer</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-ubersuggest\">8. Ubersuggest</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-8-keyword-surfer-by-surfer-seo\">9. Keyword Surfer by Surfer SEO</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-which-should-you-pick-as-the-best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool-for-you\">Which Should You Pick as the Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tool for You?</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-is-an-seo-keyword-analysis-tool\">What is an SEO Keyword Analysis Tool?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO keyword analysis tools are designed to help you get insights and data on keywords that will help you create content (or ads) that ranks and converts well. They present data such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Keyword volume</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword difficulty</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Search metrics like clicks, cost per click, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Because <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-find-long-tail-keywords-and-increase-organic-traffic/\">keyword research</a> plays a huge role in successful digital marketing campaigns, SEO keyword analysis tools are integral to any marketer&#8217;s toolbox.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-why-should-you-conduct-keyword-analysis\">Why Should You Conduct Keyword Analysis?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As mentioned above, keyword analysis is vital in running successful search marketing campaigns.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But why exactly is keyword analysis important?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A few reasons you should invest time and resources into keyword analysis include:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-drive-targeted-traffic-to-your-website\">Drive Targeted Traffic to Your Website</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most important reasons for conducting keyword analysis is that it helps you drive targeted traffic to your website. It&#8217;s essential to understand what your customers are looking for and why they&#8217;re looking for it. Both are important as they help you focus on keywords that drive relevant and targeted traffic. And using keyword research tools will help you perform an <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-perform-website-seo-analysis-on-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Perform an SEO Analysis on Your WordPress Website\">SEO analysis</a> that will help you do just that. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-notice-search-trends\">Notice Search Trends</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason keyword analysis is important is that it helps you notice search trends early. Being ahead of the curve and anticipating market behavior will ensure that you adjust your marketing efforts accordingly, thereby giving you an edge over your competitors.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-improve-conversion-rates\">Improve Conversion Rates</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword analysis is a great way to identify search intent. Understanding search intent is a crucial step to creating content that converts well. By discovering keywords that have commercial intent, you can <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-to-increase-your-organic-clickthrough-rates/\" title=\"8 Proven Ways to Increase Your Organic Clickthrough Rates\">improve your conversion rates</a> and boost your sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-the-best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool-8-amazing-tools-to-choose-from\">The Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tool: Our Top Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know why keyword analysis is so important, it&#8217;s time to go shopping. It&#8217;s time to look at the eight best SEO keyword analysis tools you should have on your radar, in no particular order.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is an excellent SEO keyword analysis tool that gives you keyword data from Google Search Console (GSC)\" class=\"wp-image-181906\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-600x267.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-135x60.png 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-203x90.png 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is a powerful yet easy-to-use SEO plugin that has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of smart business owners and marketers use it to help them boost their search engine rankings and drive qualified traffic to their sites. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many small business owners and SEOs love AIOSEO because it has powerful features that make SEO super easy. One of the most loved features in AIOSEO is the Search Statistics module. This powerful Google Search Console integration lets you track your keyword rankings and see <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-seo-data-to-boost-search-rankings/\" title=\"How to Use SEO Data to Boost Your Search Rankings \">important SEO metrics</a> with 1 click. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And the best part is you can do all this in WordPress!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To monitor your keywords, click <strong>Search Statistics <strong>»</strong> Keyword Rankings</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"288\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/search-statistics-keyword-rankings.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO\'s keyword rankings report gives you essential keyword data.\" class=\"wp-image-177217\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/search-statistics-keyword-rankings.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/search-statistics-keyword-rankings-300x123.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/search-statistics-keyword-rankings-600x246.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/search-statistics-keyword-rankings-146x60.png 146w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/search-statistics-keyword-rankings-219x90.png 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Keyword Rankings report will show you all your keywords, including those that are dropping in rankings and those going up.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"578\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/search-statistics-losing-winning.png\" alt=\"The Winning/Losing tab gives you an overview of top-performing and top-losing keywords.\" class=\"wp-image-159658\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/search-statistics-losing-winning.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/search-statistics-losing-winning-300x247.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/search-statistics-losing-winning-600x494.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/search-statistics-losing-winning-73x60.png 73w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/search-statistics-losing-winning-109x90.png 109w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides helping you see how your keywords are performing, AIOSEO’s Search Statistics module also gives you insight into your content’s performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-3.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO’s Search Statistics module also gives you insight into your content’s performance.\" class=\"wp-image-181909\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-3.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-3-300x167.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-3-600x333.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-3-108x60.png 108w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/image-3-162x90.png 162w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Content Performance report shows which <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/posts-vs-pages-in-wordpress/\" title=\"Posts vs. Pages in WordPress — Everything You Need to Know\">posts and pages</a> are performing well and which are dropping in rankings. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Search Statistics gives you a lot of keyword data you can use to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/search-statistics-power-hacks-to-help-boost-your-rankings/\" title=\"6 Search Statistics Power Hacks to Help Boost Your Rankings\">boost your search rankings</a>. This makes it one of the best keyword analysis tools for WordPress. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\">installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $49.60. A free plan is also available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-semrush\">2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush\">Semrush</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\">Semrush</a> is one of the world&#8217;s most popular SEO tools. One reason is that it&#8217;s an all-purpose SEO tool you can use to conduct any SEO research you want. One area in which it shines the most is keyword analysis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Semrush&#8217;s Keyword Overview tool offers powerful ways to get a clear picture of everything you need to know about a particular keyword. For example, it gives you insight into:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Search volume</strong>: The number of people searching for the keyword.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Keyword trend</strong>: Whether the keyword is growing in popularity or becoming less popular.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Related keywords</strong>: These are other keywords related to yours. Using them gives search engines more context about your content.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Intent</strong>. This shows the reason most searchers use your particular keyword in search. This helps you create content that meets users&#8217; search intent.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-semrush-2.png\" alt=\"Semrush is an SEO keyword analysis tool that offers a wealth of keyword data.\" class=\"wp-image-64291\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-semrush-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-semrush-2-300x120.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-semrush-2-600x240.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Apart from this, Semrush also shows you the keywords your competitors are ranking for. You also get to see keyword gaps you can exploit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you&#8217;re working on a piece of content and want to optimize it for SEO on the fly, you&#8217;ll be glad to know that AIOSEO and Semrush work together right in your WordPress dashboard. With the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/introducing-semrush-integration/\" title=\"Introducing Semrush Integration: Add Additional Keyphrases to Boost SEO\">AIOSEO and Semrush integration</a>, you can easily find more key phrases to add to your content. And you can do that with a single click.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>How much does a robust SEO keyword analysis tool like Semrush cost?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Expect to pay $99.95/month for the base plan if you pay annually</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-ahrefs\">3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ahrefs\">Ahrefs</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\">Ahrefs</a> is another SEO keyword tool you should consider adding to your tool stack.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ahrefs is similar to Semrush in many ways when it comes to its set of keyword analysis tools. The Keyword Explorer feature is an excellent tool for discovering keywords for your content. </p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"324\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ahrefs-2.png\" alt=\"Ahrefs is another powerful SEO keyword analysis tool that should be on your radar.  \" class=\"wp-image-64334\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ahrefs-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ahrefs-2-300x139.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ahrefs-2-600x278.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Besides discovering new keywords, Keyword Explorer also gives you insight into:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Keywords your competitors are ranking for</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword movement</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Other keywords your top-ranking pages rank for</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Number of clicks on search results containing your keyword</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides being an SEO keyword analysis tool, you can use Ahrefs for many other SEO-related tasks, such as <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/showcase/best-backlink-checker-tools-compared/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">backlink analysis</a>, site audits, rank tracking, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing for Ahrefs starts at $99/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-serpstat\">4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Serpstat\">Serpstat</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a feature-rich SEO keyword analysis tool that won&#8217;t cost as much as the first two on our list, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\">Serpstat</a> is it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Serpstat is a powerful SEO tool trusted by many big brands for its versatility and ease of use. When it comes to SEO keyword analysis, you couldn&#8217;t get a better tool. For one, it makes it easy to see how you rank for your keywords, how your competitors rank, and the content that occupies SERP features. Serpstat also gives you a graphical representation of historical user interest for that keyword. This helps give you a better overview of your keyword. If you&#8217;re running PPC campaigns, it also shows you the ads that are ranking high.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/serpstat/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-serpstat-2.png\" alt=\"Serpstat is another keyword analysis tool to consider thanks to being data and feature-rich.\" class=\"wp-image-64517\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-serpstat-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-serpstat-2-300x219.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-serpstat-2-600x439.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>One other advantage Serpstat has is the simple and easy-to-understand dashboard. It&#8217;s so intuitive even beginners can easily find their way around.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As for pricing, Serpstat&#8217;s paid plans start at $69/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-kwfinder-by-mangools\">5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"KWFinder by Mangools\">KWFinder by Mangools</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"KWFinder by Mangools\">KWFinder by Mangools</a> is another SEO keyword tool that should be on your radar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like Semrush and Ahrefs, KWFinder allows you to research keywords by domain, geographical location, language, and more. These allow you to zero in on the data you need to power your campaigns. The tool also gives you a clear overview of the SERPs for your chosen keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like Serpstat, KWFinder has an intuitive dashboard that makes navigating to the different reports you need easy.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-kwfinder-2.png\" alt=\"KWFinder is an SEO keyword analysis tool that comes with a simple and easy to use dashboard.\" class=\"wp-image-64297\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-kwfinder-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-kwfinder-2-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-kwfinder-2-600x274.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Pricing for Mangools&#8217; base plan is $29.90. That&#8217;s a juicy offer for a tool that offers you some of the best features you need to execute effective SEO campaigns.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-5-long-tail-pro\">6. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/long-tail-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Long Tail Pro\">Long Tail Pro</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As the name suggests, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/long-tail-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Long Tail Pro\">Long Tail Pro</a> was designed to help marketers find long-tail keywords to help them rank.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like the other SEO keyword analysis tools on our list, Long Tail Pro offers tons of data on your keywords and those your competitors are ranking for. This is data such as keyword suggestions with metrics, keyword rankings, and much more.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/long-tail-pro/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-long-tail-pro-2.png\" alt=\"Long Tail Pro is a keyword analysis tool that\'s easy to understand and versatile.\" class=\"wp-image-64515\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-long-tail-pro-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-long-tail-pro-2-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-keyword-analysis-tool-long-tail-pro-2-600x274.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Designed to help websites rank, Long Tail Pro is a great tool to help you find easy-to-rank-for keywords. A cool feature you&#8217;ll appreciate is that Long Tail Pro color-codes keywords according to search difficulty. The color coding makes it easier to see at a glance whether your chosen keyword is easy to rank for or not.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As for pricing, Long Tail Pro&#8217;s bottom-tier plan costs $27/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-6-moz-keyword-explorer\">7. <a href=\"https://moz.com/explorer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Moz Keyword Explorer\">Moz Keyword Explorer</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://moz.com/explorer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Moz</a> is a name that has almost become synonymous with SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moz has been in the game for a long time and has established itself as a thought leader. Because of these two facts, they&#8217;ve managed to build an SEO keyword analysis tool that ranks among the best. With Moz&#8217;s <a href=\"https://moz.com/explorer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Moz Keyword Explorer\">Keyword Explorer</a>, you can easily conduct:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Competitive keyword analysis</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sort keywords by predictive metrics (like search volume, difficulty, cost-per-click, e.t.c.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Analyze SERPs according to your keyword</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Use various criteria to filter out irrelevant keywords</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://moz.com/explorer\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-moz-2.png\" alt=\"Moz is an SEO keyword analysis tool that gives a comprehensive overview of your chosen keyword. \" class=\"wp-image-64309\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-moz-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-moz-2-300x188.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-moz-2-600x376.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Exporting your keywords into well-formatted CSV files for further analysis is also super-easy. And having been in the business for a long time, Moz has an advanced engine that shows more accurate search metrics than other tools on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing-wise, Moz will set you back $99/month for the base plan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-7-ubersuggest\">8. <a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ubersuggest\">Ubersuggest</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Starting out and looking for a keyword analysis tool that won&#8217;t break the bank?<br>Meet <a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Ubersuggest\">Ubersuggest</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ubersuggest offers a lot of important SEO keyword analysis data, such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Search volume data</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword suggestions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Keyword difficulty</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Estimated traffic</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/ubersuggest/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"755\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ubersugest-2.png\" alt=\"Ubersuggest is an SEO keyword analysis tool that\'s becoming popular for its in-depth keyword analysis.\" class=\"wp-image-64311\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ubersugest-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ubersugest-2-278x300.png 278w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-ubersugest-2-600x647.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Ubersuggest also gives you the average number of backlinks you&#8217;ll need to rank for that keyword. Despite being relatively new on the market, Ubersuggest is fast becoming a force to reckon with in the SEO keyword analysis tool space.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, how much will this budget-friendly SEO keyword analysis tool cost you?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ubersuggest&#8217;s lowest-tier plan costs only $12/month and is suited for those running up to three websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-8-keyword-surfer-by-surfer-seo\">9. <a href=\"https://surferseo.com/keyword-surfer-extension/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Keyword Surfer by Surfer SEO\">Keyword Surfer by Surfer SEO</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://surferseo.com/keyword-surfer-extension/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Keyword Surfer by Surfer SEO\">Keyword Surfer</a> differs from the other SEO keyword analysis tools on our list in two ways. First, it&#8217;s a Chrome-based tool. Secondly, it&#8217;s more geared towards on-page content optimization.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword Surfer offers insights into keyword data such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Average search volume</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Related keywords</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Questions featured in the top-ranking content</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Surfer&#8217;s Chrome extension is an excellent tool for getting instant insights into your keyword and the content ranking high for it:</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://surferseo.com/keyword-surfer-extension/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"318\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-keyword-finder-2.png\" alt=\"Keyword Finder by Surfer SEO is an excellent SEO keyword analysis for content optimization.\" class=\"wp-image-64321\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-keyword-finder-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-keyword-finder-2-300x136.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/seo-keyword-analysis-tool-keyword-finder-2-600x273.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Compared to the other SEO keyword analysis tools on the list, Keyword Surfer is pretty basic. But it&#8217;s a great tool to have handy if you want to do keyword research on the fly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The price tag on Keyword Surfer is $34/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-which-should-you-pick-as-the-best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool-for-you\">Which Should You Pick as the Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tool for You?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for an SEO keyword analysis tool that gives you GSC keyword performance data right in WordPress, then we recommend <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a>. Plus, it has many other features to help you act on your keyword data to boost your search rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if you need a tool to help with keyword research, then we recommend <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ahrefs\">Ahrefs</a>. It has all the features you need to run complete SEO campaigns.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article has helped you know which SEO keyword analysis tool is best for you. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2023\">ultimate WordPress SEO guide</a> or our guide to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-start-a-small-business-blog/\" title=\"How to Start a Small Business Blog in 2023\">starting a small business blog</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/\">9 Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tools You Need to Know in 2023</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"How to Use the Google Snippet Preview to Boost Your SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:156:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 20 Apr 2023 16:27:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Google snippet preview\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"SERP snippet preview\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=177317\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:430:\"<p>Would you like to learn how to use the Google snippet preview to boost your SEO? The preview is a picture of your page in Google search results. By using a preview, you can find and fix errors before publishing.&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo/\">How to Use the Google Snippet Preview to Boost Your SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34064:\"<p>Would you like to learn how to use the Google snippet preview to boost your SEO?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The preview is a picture of your page in Google search results. By using a preview, you can find and fix errors before publishing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this step-by-step tutorial, we&#8217;ll share an easy way to use a Google snippet preview to optimize your SEO. And we&#8217;ll provide some snippet tips that&#8217;ll put you ahead of the game.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-why-use-a-google-snippet-preview\">Why Use a Google Snippet Preview?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-download-the-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-plugin\">Step 1: Download the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Plugin</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-find-the-google-snippet-preview\">Step 2: Find the Google Snippet Preview</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-3-optimize-your-title\">Step 3: Optimize Your Title</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-4-optimize-your-description\">Step 4: Optimize Your Description</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-5-optimize-your-slug\">Step 5: Optimize Your Slug</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-why-use-a-google-snippet-preview\">Why Use a Google Snippet Preview?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We all know how standard search engine results look. There&#8217;s a title, a link, and a description. In SEO, we call that a &#8220;search snippet.&#8221; It looks like this:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"918\" height=\"208\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet.png\" alt=\"standard google search snippet\" class=\"wp-image-180522\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet.png 918w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-300x68.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-768x174.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-600x136.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-190x43.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/google-search-snippet-397x90.png 397w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But sometimes, the title gets cut off, as in this example below.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"233\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-1024x233.png\" alt=\"truncated title in serp\" class=\"wp-image-177440\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-1024x233.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-300x68.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-768x174.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-600x136.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-190x43.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated-396x90.png 396w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/11-serp-title-truncated.png 1206w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Or the snippet may not provide a clear description of the article.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Problems like this can cause people to skip your article. And that makes it hard to get new readers or sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Previews provide a simple way to improve your snippet so that it drives more click-throughs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And one of the easiest ways to access and edit previews is to use an <strong>SEO plugin</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-1-download-the-all-in-one-seo-aioseo-plugin\">Step 1: Download the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) Plugin</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend you download and install the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is an established plugin that&#8217;s beginner-friendly. <br><br>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) has thousands of 5-star ratings on WordPress.org, and over 3 million people are currently using it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After downloading AIOSEO in your WordPress editor:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Plugins » Add New</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Upload the zip file</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click <strong>Activate</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>A setup wizard will open and walk you through a few easy steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Questions? Check out our<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installation-instructions-for-wordpress-com-users/\"> installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-2-find-the-google-snippet-preview\">Step 2: Find the Google Snippet Preview</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, in your WordPress editor, navigate to a page or post that you want to see a Google snippet preview of.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-option-1-start-from-wordpress-preview-mode\">Option 1: Start From WordPress Preview Mode</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re in WordPress preview mode, hover your mouse over the AIOSEO icon in the admin bar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the drop-down that appears, select <strong>SEO Preview</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1022\" height=\"244\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1.png\" alt=\"aioseo seo preview menu\" class=\"wp-image-180526\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1.png 1022w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-300x72.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-768x183.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-600x143.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-190x45.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/3-aioseo-seo-preview-1-377x90.png 377w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you can see your Google SERP snippet preview:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"574\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-1024x574.png\" alt=\"aioseo google snippet preview\" class=\"wp-image-177332\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-1024x574.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-300x168.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-768x431.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-704x396.png 704w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-600x336.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-107x60.png 107w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window-160x90.png 160w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/4-SEO-preview-window.png 1118w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to change your title or description, click the gray <strong>Edit Snippet</strong> button. Then follow the instructions in <strong>Steps 2</strong> and <strong>3</strong>.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-option-2-start-from-editing-mode\">Option 2: Start From Editing Mode</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re in <strong>WordPress editing mode</strong>, do the following.</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>In the upper right corner, click on the <strong>AIOSEO button</strong>. (That will open AIOSEO settings in your right-hand navigation column.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Then click <strong>General.</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"725\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-1024x725.png\" alt=\"aioseo settings\" class=\"wp-image-177334\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-1024x725.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-300x212.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-768x544.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-600x425.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-85x60.png 85w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview-127x90.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/5-aioseo-find-google-snippet-preview.png 1040w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you&#8217;ll see your Google snippet preview.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"435\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-1024x435.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo google snippet preview sidebar\" class=\"wp-image-177456\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-1024x435.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-300x127.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-768x326.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-1536x653.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-2048x870.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-600x255.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-141x60.jpg 141w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-snippet-preview-right-column-212x90.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This snippet preview is narrow and simulates what your article would look like on a smartphone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-how-to-toggle-between-the-desktop-and-mobile-preview\">How to Toggle Between the Desktop and Mobile Preview</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Beneath the snippet preview, click the edit button to see a desktop preview.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"646\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-1024x646.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo edit google snippet preview\" class=\"wp-image-177333\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-1024x646.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-300x189.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-768x485.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-600x379.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-95x60.jpg 95w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview-143x90.jpg 143w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/6-edit-google-snippet-preview.jpg 1090w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A small pop-up window will appear. Notice that your snippet preview is wider. The preview is now simulating what your page would look like for someone doing a desktop Google search.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"487\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-1024x487.png\" alt=\"aioseo google snippet preview desktop mode\" class=\"wp-image-177335\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-1024x487.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-300x143.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-768x365.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-600x285.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-126x60.png 126w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview-189x90.png 189w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/7-desktop-google-snippet-preview.png 1117w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can toggle between desktop and mobile snippet previews by clicking the device icons in the upper right area of the pop-up window.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"477\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-1024x477.png\" alt=\"google snippet preview device toggle \" class=\"wp-image-177336\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-1024x477.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-768x358.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-600x280.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-129x60.png 129w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview-193x90.png 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/8-toggle-google-snippet-preview.png 1105w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know where to find the Google snippet preview let&#8217;s explore the <strong>Post Title</strong> field.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-3-optimize-your-title\">Step 3: Optimize Your Title</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Below the Google snippet preview, you&#8217;ll see a <strong>Post</strong> <strong>Title</strong> section.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s how it looks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"952\" height=\"312\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field.png\" alt=\"aioseo preview snippet editor\" class=\"wp-image-180529\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field.png 952w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-300x98.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-768x252.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-600x197.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-183x60.png 183w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-field-275x90.png 275w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll see 3 small gray boxes (or &#8220;tags&#8221;) in the Post Title field.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"952\" height=\"293\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags.png\" alt=\"aioseo post title tags\" class=\"wp-image-180527\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags.png 952w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-300x92.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-768x236.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-600x185.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-190x58.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-tags-292x90.png 292w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s what those gray tags do.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>The <strong>Post Title </strong>tag automatically pulls in the title you typed at the top of your article.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The <strong>Separator </strong>tag automatically adds a customizable separator character (like a dash or a pipe) after your title.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>The <strong>Site Title</strong> tag automatically pulls in the name of your website.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These tags can save time because you don&#8217;t need to type any content in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default in AIOSEO, this is how all your Post Title fields are set up.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But you can remove the <strong>Site Title</strong> and <strong>Separator</strong> and use all 60 characters just for your article title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s look at two cases where you might want to change the default settings of the Post Title.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-case-1-you-want-to-shorten-your-title\">Case #1: You Want to Shorten Your Title</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In our example preview below, our title is over the recommended 60 characters. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Note that the <strong>Separator</strong> and <strong>Site Title</strong> (plus the spaces in between) are part of that 60-character count.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"641\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-1024x641.png\" alt=\"aioseo post title over character limit\" class=\"wp-image-177441\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-1024x641.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-300x188.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-768x480.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-600x375.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-96x60.png 96w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit-144x90.png 144w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/12-title-over-recommended-character-limit.png 1111w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what to do?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You could remove the <strong>Separator</strong> and <strong>Site Title</strong> tags. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>(You can always add them by clicking the &#8220;spares&#8221; at the upper right.)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"949\" height=\"550\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor.png\" alt=\"aioseo post title tag removal\" class=\"wp-image-180532\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor.png 949w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-300x174.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-768x445.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-600x348.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-104x60.png 104w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-preview-snippet-editor-155x90.png 155w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Notice in the example above that our title is still over the recommended 60 characters.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By removing the word &#8220;Downloadable,&#8221; our title now fits within the recommendations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: to change your title, either edit the title directly on the article page, or, delete the gray Post Title tag from the field, and type in your preferred title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We did the latter in this case below:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"950\" height=\"492\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60.png\" alt=\"aioseo post title under character limit\" class=\"wp-image-180533\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60.png 950w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-300x155.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-768x398.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-600x311.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-116x60.png 116w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-post-title-under-60-174x90.png 174w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-case-2-we-want-to-use-all-available-space-for-our-title\">Case #2: We want to use all available space for our title</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let&#8217;s imagine that our title, separator, and site title combined are within the recommended 60-character limit. Here&#8217;s a made-up example:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How to Replace a Toilet (5 steps) &#8211; Monongahela Hardware</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>But the site name takes up a lot of space.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We might want to get rid of the separator and site title just so we can add more words to our title, like so:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>How to Replace a Toilet (5 steps) &#8211; [DIY or Hire us]</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The headline above gives the searcher more information: It&#8217;s not just a DIY article. You can hire this hardware store to do this job for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>If the site owner has set up <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/a-complete-local-seo-checklist/\">local SEO</a>, then this article will show up for local searches for &#8220;how to replace a toilet.&#8221;</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you understand the default settings for the Post Title field. And you know you can change these or manually type in a title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at exactly how your title affects SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-title-seo-factors\">Title SEO Factors</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Titles can have a significant impact on click-through rates. Here are 3 ways to prep your title for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-include-a-focus-keyword\">Include a Focus Keyword</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s important to include your <strong>focus keyword </strong>in your SEO title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/using-the-focus-keyphrase-to-analyze-your-content/\">focus keyword</a> helps Google understand what search queries your article should appear in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can think of the focus keyword as the <strong>main topic</strong> of your article. (New to keyword research? Check out this great <a href=\"https://www.blogtyrant.com/how-to-easily-find-the-best-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">beginner&#8217;s guide</a>.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some examples of focus keywords included in titles.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>8 Best <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">WordPress FAQ Block</span> Plugins</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Go Paperless</span> in 7 Steps</li>\n\n\n\n<li>9 Best <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Clickfunnels Replacements</span> Free and Paid</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">OptinMonster Review</span> 2023: Is it the Best Tool for Growth?</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-persuasive-text\">Persuasive Text</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Your title should be clear and descriptive. Along with the page description (discussed below), your title is one of your biggest opportunities to get click-throughs. It should give searchers an excellent reason to click.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But don&#8217;t over-promise. Write a title that tells the searcher what they can expect from your web page.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-title-length-is-the-number-of-characters-important\">Title Length: Is the Number of Characters Important?</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We mentioned that the AIOSEO snippet preview tool recommends capping titles at 60 characters.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But here&#8217;s some nuance. There are cases where you may want to use titles that are <strong>longer</strong>. Marketers often do.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s see why. In the example below, this article has a 66-character-long title. The article is displayed as a &#8220;featured snippet.&#8221; Because of the large display area, the full title is shown (at the top).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"954\" height=\"510\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length.png\" alt=\"featured snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-180535\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length.png 954w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-300x160.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-768x411.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-600x321.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-112x60.png 112w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/featured-snippet-title-length-168x90.png 168w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But only some articles wind up as featured snippets. The key benefit of using a long title is you can <strong>include additional keywords</strong> for search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you try this, make sure that what appears in the first 60 or so characters is a complete title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s move on to your description.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-4-optimize-your-description\">Step 4: Optimize Your Description</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Returning to the Google snippet preview, scroll past the <strong>Post Title,</strong> and you&#8217;ll see a <strong>Meta Description</strong> area.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here we recommend that you remove the <strong>Excerpt</strong> tag. It&#8217;s just a placeholder that tells Google to pull any excerpt from your page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because you get 160 characters for your description, you&#8217;ll want to craft it yourself.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Be sure to include your focus keyword.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Try to include a few related keywords.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In the example below, &#8220;create a digital strategy&#8221; is our focus keyword (or main article topic). We&#8217;ve added the words &#8220;traffic, conversions, and revenue&#8221; because these are 3 things people hope to achieve with a digital strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then we added some &#8220;bonus&#8221; information at the end.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-1024x347.png\" alt=\"aioseo meta description field\" class=\"wp-image-180536\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-1024x347.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-300x102.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-768x261.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-600x204.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-177x60.png 177w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description-265x90.png 265w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/aioseo-optimize-meta-description.png 1117w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-meta-description-seo-factors\">Meta Description SEO Factors</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let&#8217;s review the main SEO factors for your meta description. It’s important to realize that meta descriptions are not ranking factors, but they can boost your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-focus-keyword-presence\">Focus Keyword Presence</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Your focus keyword should be in your meta description. And you can include related keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can find related keywords by doing a Chrome Incognito search using your focus keyword or by using a free tool like Ubersuggest.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-informative-and-persuasive-text\">Informative and Persuasive Text</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Ask yourself: “What’s unique or valuable about my article? How is it different from others on the same subject?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like your title, this is a significant opportunity to win click-throughs with a precise summary.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-emojis\">Emojis</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You can put <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-emojis-to-your-wordpress-blog/\">emojis</a> in your meta description or title. Emojis aren’t a ranking factor, but they are eye-catching. For that reason, they may increase click-throughs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll need to experiment to see if this is the case with your content. But make sure emojis are a good fit with your brand voice first.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"193\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-1024x193.png\" alt=\"emoji in search snippet \" class=\"wp-image-180538\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-1024x193.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-300x57.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-768x145.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-600x113.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-190x36.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title-477x90.png 477w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/emojis-in-serp-title.png 1113w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-step-5-optimize-your-slug\">Step 5: Optimize Your Slug</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A slug is the last part of a URL. A forward slash precedes it:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">example.com/blog/<strong>hello-world</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the example above, &#8220;hello-world&#8221; is the slug.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, WordPress automatically generates a slug for each post you create. It simply copies the title of your post. So a post called &#8220;This is My First Blog Post&#8221; would generate this slug:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">example.com/blog/<strong>this-is-my-first-blog-post</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-include-your-focus-keyword\">Include Your Focus Keyword</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that you include your focus keyword in your slug.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll be fine if you include your keyword in the title. But if you want to edit your slug, you can click the gear icon at the upper right. Then go to <strong>Post » Permalink.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll see a URL slug field. Just type your preferred slug there.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"401\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-1024x401.png\" alt=\"wordpress edit url slug\" class=\"wp-image-180539\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-1024x401.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-300x118.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-768x301.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-600x235.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-153x60.png 153w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug-230x90.png 230w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/wordpress-edit-url-slug.png 1105w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-a-few-extra-notes\">A Few Extra Notes</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>SEO tools: </strong>Now that you’re using the All in One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin, explore some easy SEO wins like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/adding-breadcrumbs-to-your-site-using-the-aioseo-breadcrumbs-block/\" title=\"\">adding breadcrumbs</a> or a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/wordpress-table-of-contents-seo/#aioseo-quick-start-guide-add-a-table-of-contents-now\" title=\"\">table of contents</a> to your pages. That can improve user experience too.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Pixels</strong>: Some websites say you need to measure your titles by pixels. This isn&#8217;t true. It&#8217;s a rumor that spread after a Google employee made a related <a href=\"https://twitter.com/danbri/status/1376808127241289730\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">joke</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>What’s Google SERP?</strong> SERP (or SERPs) stands for search engine results pages. Put “Google” in front of that and the phrase refers specifically to Google’s search engine results pages.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>What’s a SERP simulator</strong>? This is the same thing as a Google snippet preview. There are lots of names for this including SERP snippet preview tool or Google SERP snippet optimization tool. </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What&#8217;s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Small tweaks to your title and description can have an outsized impact.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you understand the benefit of using the AIOSEO plugin to optimize Google snippet previews in WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And check out our article on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/small-business-seo-scams-how-to-detect-and-avoid-them/\" title=\"\">how to avoid SEO scams</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-wordpress-faq-block-to-boost-seo-and-get-more-traffic/\" title=\"\">how to use FAQs strategically</a> to drive more traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo/\">How to Use the Google Snippet Preview to Boost Your SEO</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-google-snippet-preview-to-boost-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"15+ Best 