r, leading to faster and better search engine rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to use AI SEO software tools to boost your rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-ai-seo\">What is AI SEO?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-use-ai-seo-software-to-boost-your-search-rankings\">How to Use AI SEO Software to Boost Your Search Rankings</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-use-the-right-ai-seo-tools\">1. Use the Right AI SEO Software</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-boost-organic-ctr-on-serps-using-ai\">2. Boost Organic CTR on SERPs Using AI Software</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-build-internal-links-for-topical-authority-and-better-rankings\">3. Build Internal Links for Topical Authority and Better Rankings</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-discover-hidden-ranking-opportunities\">4. Discover Hidden Ranking Opportunities</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-optimize-your-content-more-effectively\">5. Optimize Your Content More Effectively</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-ai-seo-software-giving-you-the-edge-you-need-to-outrank-your-competitors\">AI SEO Software: Giving You the Edge You Need to Outrank Your Competitors</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-what-is-ai-seo\">What is AI SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To best understand AI SEO (not to be confused with AIOSEO), let&#8217;s briefly examine what these 2 acronyms mean.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Artificial intelligence (AI) is an umbrella term that covers several different technologies, including machine learning (ML), natural language processing (NLP), deep learning, computer vision and other emerging technologies. These technologies are designed to help machines perform specific cognitive tasks as well as or better than humans.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the other hand, search engine optimization (SEO) enhances your website and web pages to drive free organic traffic from search engines like Google. With SEO, your goal is to follow <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\" title=\"SEO Best Practices: 20 Ultimate SEO Tips to Boost Rankings\">WordPress SEO best practices</a> on your site. Doing so helps search engines easily discover your content and display it in the search results.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AI SEO, therefore, is using AI technology to optimize your website and content for search engines and users. Doing so helps you easily scale your SEO campaigns and execute tasks faster and more efficiently. As a result, your chances of ranking high on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs) are bolstered.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-use-ai-seo-software-to-boost-your-search-rankings\">How to Use AI SEO Software to Boost Your Search Rankings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know what AI SEO is and its benefits, let’s quickly look at ways you can use it to boost your search rankings.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-use-the-right-ai-seo-tools\">1. Use the Right AI SEO Software</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>First, to boost your SEO using AI, you must use the right <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-ai-seo-tools-for-wordpress/\" title=\"The 7 Best AI SEO Tools for WordPress in 2023\">AI SEO software</a>. A great example is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is one of the best SEO plugins on the market.\" class=\"wp-image-170372\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo-600x267.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo-135x60.png 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/aioseo-203x90.png 203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is the best WordPress SEO plugin on the market and has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of savvy website owners and marketers trust the plugin to help them dominate SERPs and drive relevant site traffic. This is because the plugin has many <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">powerful SEO features and modules</a> to help you optimize your website for search engines and users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides being the best WordPress SEO plugin, AIOSEO also boasts powerful AI-powered features to help you easily optimize your site for better search rankings. Examples include the AI Title/Description Generator and Link Assistant, which we’ll discuss in the sections below.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">detailed installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-boost-organic-ctr-on-serps-using-ai\">2. Boost Organic CTR on SERPs Using AI Software</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-to-increase-your-organic-clickthrough-rates/\" title=\"8 Proven Ways to Increase Your Organic Clickthrough Rates\">Boosting your organic clickthrough rate</a> (CTR) on SERPs is a great way to use AI in your SEO campaigns. One of the best ways to do this is to optimize your SEO titles and meta descriptions. This is because these are some of the first elements of your search listing users see on SERPs and impact the way users interact with your search listings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO’s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt/\" title=\"Our OpenAI Integration Just Got 10x More Affordable – Now Using ChatGPT!\">AI Title/Description Generator</a> is one of the best AI-powered SEO tools for this.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"699\" height=\"353\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1.png\" alt=\"You can use AI SEO software to craft meta data that can help you boost your CTR.\" class=\"wp-image-174239\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1.png 699w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/seo-title-generator-1-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This powerful tool helps you automatically generate SEO titles and meta descriptions, saving you precious time.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And because these are generated from your content, they’re also optimized for SEO. Plus, you can choose from 5 suggestions, making it easier to get the meta description or SEO title that suits your article best.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"462\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples.png\" alt=\"Generating meta-descriptions is super easy with AIOSEO\'s AI Title/Description Generator.\" class=\"wp-image-170248\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-300x197.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-600x395.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-91x60.png 91w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-137x90.png 137w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Using AI to automatically generate SEO titles and meta descriptions is a great time saver, especially when you need to do so at scale.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress\">Check out this article</a> for more details on enabling this powerful feature in AIOSEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-build-internal-links-for-topical-authority-and-better-rankings\">3. Build Internal Links for Topical Authority and Better Rankings</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another way to boost your search engine rankings is to build strategic internal links. If your website has many pages, manually doing so can be <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-link-assistant-can-save-you-time-on-internal-and-external-link-building/\" title=\"6 Ways Link Assistant Can Save You Time On Internal Link Building\">laborious and time-consuming</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And you can solve this problem by using AI to build your internal links automatically.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where AIOSEO’s AI-powered <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/internal-link-assistant/\" title=\"Link Assistant\">Link Assistant</a> shines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Link Assistant, you get an overview of all the links on your site via the Links Report.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"381\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report.png\" alt=\"To help boost your internal linking strategy, Link Assistant\" class=\"wp-image-79017\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report-300x163.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-links-report-600x327.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Link Assistant also shows you linking opportunities and enables you to create links between your posts and pages without opening them in the WordPress Editor. You can even edit the anchor text and optimize your link placement.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"354\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-1024x354.png\" alt=\"Link Assistant enables you to edit anchor text.\" class=\"wp-image-79022\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-1024x354.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-300x104.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-768x266.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1-600x208.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/internal-linking-with-link-assistant-markup-1.png 1078w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you have orphaned pages on your site, Link Assistant shows these to you and enables you to create links to them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Building internal links is critical to boosting your SEO as it leads to <a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/blog/topical-authority/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">topical authority</a>. It also makes it easier for search engines to crawl and index your content. Both result in higher rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-link-assistant-to-optimize-your-internal-linking-strategy/\" title=\"How to Use Link Assistant to Optimize Your Internal Linking Strategy\">Check out this detailed tutorial</a> for a step-by-step guide on using Link Assistant to boost your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-discover-hidden-ranking-opportunities\">4. Discover Hidden Ranking Opportunities&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Keyword research and content gap discovery are essential to ranking high on SERPs and outranking your competitors. However, finding ranking opportunities is becoming more challenging as SEO has become a very competitive marketing channel.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Again, this is where AI can help you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using AI can help you find hidden ranking opportunities much faster than you would by using traditional SEO tools. They can help you find keyword opportunities your competitors are not exploiting, giving you a better chance of outranking them and getting the lion’s share of traffic. They can also help you discover what’s working for the top-ranking content regarding keywords, phrases, and questions that are low-hanging fruit.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A great example of this is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/frase-io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Frase\">Frase</a>. This powerful AI-powered tool helps you create optimized content briefs designed to help you create content that ranks well.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you’re looking for a great way to get to the top of the SERPs, use AI SEO software to find hidden ranking opportunities.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-5-optimize-your-content-more-effectively\">5. Optimize Your Content More Effectively</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Content optimization is the process of finetuning your content to stand a better chance of ranking high on SERPs. Doing so manually is laborious, especially when you need to produce a lot of content.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s why you should use AI SEO software to do this.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Examples of AI-powered content optimization tools include Semrush’s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush-seo-writing-assistant/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush Writing Assistant\">SEO Writing Assistant</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/surfer-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Surfer SEO\">SurferSEO</a>. These will help you know:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Which keywords to include in your content</li>\n\n\n\n<li>&nbsp;The questions users are asking</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Content gaps to exploit</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps you create content that’s easily discoverable by search engines. It also helps ensure your content meets search intent.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-ai-seo-software-giving-you-the-edge-you-need-to-outrank-your-competitors\">AI SEO Software: Giving You the Edge You Need to Outrank Your Competitors&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>AI SEO software offers excellent tools for designing and deploying SEO campaigns quickly. As a result, you get to rank faster and drive more traffic to your site.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article has helped you learn how to use AI SEO software to boost your rankings. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2023\">ultimate WordPress SEO guide</a> or our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-technical-seo-the-best-checklist-in-2022/\" title=\"What Is Technical SEO? The Best Checklist in 2023\">technical SEO checklist</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-ai-seo-software-to-boost-rankings/\">How to Use AI SEO Software to Boost Your Rankings</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-ai-seo-software-to-boost-rankings/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:24:\"https://aioseo.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:48:\"WpOrg\\Requests\\Utility\\CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:18:{s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Wed, 03 May 2023 08:10:10 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xm